WITH deduped_billing_events AS (
  SELECT 
    subscription_id,
    event_month,
    amount,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY subscription_id, event_month ORDER BY event_id) AS rn
  FROM billing_events
),
sub_with_data AS (
  SELECT 
    s.subscription_id,
    s.user_id,
    s.plan_id,
    s.started_at,
    s.ended_at,
    s.status,
    COALESCE(p.tier, 'Unknown') AS tier,
    COALESCE(c.industry, 'Unknown') AS industry
  FROM subscriptions s
  LEFT JOIN users u ON s.user_id = u.user_id
  LEFT JOIN companies c ON u.company_id = c.company_id
  LEFT JOIN plans p ON s.plan_id = p.plan_id
)
SELECT 
  sd.subscription_id,
  sd.user_id,
  sd.plan_id,
  sd.started_at,
  sd.ended_at,
  sd.status,
  sd.tier,
  sd.industry,
  be.event_month,
  be.amount
FROM sub_with_data sd
LEFT JOIN deduped_billing_events be ON sd.subscription_id = be.subscription_id AND be.rn = 1;
